        <sponsor name-id="C001036">Mrs. Capps</sponsor> (for herself, <cosponsor name-id="M001160">Ms. Moore</cosponsor>, <cosponsor name-id="H001050">Ms. Hanabusa</cosponsor>, and <cosponsor name-id="L000287">Mr. Lewis</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was referred to the <committee-name committee-id="HJU00">Committee on the Judiciary</committee-name>
